            "fi-fi": {
              "display_title": "JAWBLADE",
              "description": "”Varoitus! JAWBLADE on karannut Hero Factorystä vesiplaneetta Scyllalle. Sen murskaavat leuat, terävät evät ja magmaterät ovat siellä elementissään, mutta uskomme, että pystytte tuomaan tuon isoksi venähtäneen nuijapään takaisin Hero Factoryyn. Onnea matkaan!”",
              "title": "JAWBLADE",
              "tags": []
            },
            "en-us": {
              "bullet_points": "•  Features power jaw, razor fins and magma blades\r\n•  Highly flexible and poseable elements\r\n•  Operate the crushing jaws!\r\n•  Includes unique code worth 200 game points for LEGO Hero Factory BREAKOUT game\r\n•  Battle with hero 6293 FURNO!\r\n•  Combine with 6293 FURNO for an even bigger model!\r\n•  Over 11” (30cm) long",
              "display_title": "JAWBLADE",
              "description": "“Warning! JAWBLADE has broken out of the Hero Factory and has escaped to water planet Scylla. With crushing jaws, razor fins and magma blades, he’s really in his element. You can cuff him and return that overgrown tadpole to the Hero Factory! Good luck!”",
              "title": "JAWBLADE",
              "headline": "Swim rings around the heroes with JAWBLADE and his magma blades!",
